    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6552889/" class="title-link">【笔记】只要加入了我们，就是我们中的一员。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6552889"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
